Module chav1961.purelib

Package chav1961.purelib.streams.char2byte

This package contains a set of output streams, that get character content and convert it to the appropriative byte content. All the classes in the packages are children of the Writer and can be used in all cases when the one is used.

Since:
0.0.1 last change 0.0.2
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
